statement.markdown:
You are given a node of a singly linked list. Your task is to traverse the linked list and print the data of each node. A node in a singly linked list is represented as follows: 

```
class Node {
    int data;
    Node next;
    public Node(int data) {
        this.data = data;
        this.next = null;
    }
}
```

You will be given the head node of the linked list. You have to print the data of each node in the list. For example, if the linked list is 1 -> 2 -> 3 -> 4 -> 5, you should print:

```
1
2
3
4
5
```

